{"tid":1659417,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"(大胆 !) 張建宗稱電光火石間警察很難全部跟足規則做事","createTime":"2019-10-17T02:43:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-17T03:37:16.000Z","uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"4f876619d7c7c8d5a5f89162010696590b2497e3","tid":1659417,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T02:43:49.000Z","msg":"政務司司長張建宗回應警察被指使用過分暴力時稱，在電光火石，好難要全部跟足規則做事，不會批評警方的行動部署，認為對警察有不滿，已有機制全面處理。<br />\n<br />\n張建宗出席商台節目時，回應施政報告未有談及警民關係的問題，他表示，施政報告主要是談及民生問題，警民關係不是著眼點，但不等如不重要，又說監警會已做了很多工作，年底亦會向特首提交首份報告。<br />\n<br />\n被問到有否準備要再上一層樓出任特首，張建宗表示，今日主題不是回應這個話題，強調問責團隊要有合作精神。再被追問如果有需要，是否願意接任，張建宗回應表示，假設問題現階段不回應，當務之急要讓香港走回正軌，再被問到是否在接任問題上不會「關後門」，他表示，不會評論這個問題，又讚揚特首林鄭月娥是相當能幹。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1486677-20191017.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1486677-20191017.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=o%2BN67aGUGKsADGfJqajrgDHxASuYsPIDBrSRMhTQaAk%3D&h=4e508070\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1486677-20191017.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=3d6d8a9b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1486677-20191017.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"2a19c1c692534853dc6feca0cfc098ad89029e8c","tid":1659417,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T02:44:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jwJzHzo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjwJzHzo.jpg&h=eb217258&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"5ec8daabdab85644e7126a8f2860c5b713c42d8f","tid":1659417,"uid":312125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T02:45:21.000Z","msg":"太監<br />\n<br />\n【行動】西九遊行<span style=\"color: red;\">需大量針對強國人文宣</span>！<br />\n務求<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">輸出革命</span></strong>！附詳盡策略：<br />\n<a href=\"https://